- The integer result is the maximum `k`-repeating value of the string `word` in the string `sequence`.
- The string parameter `word` must be a substring of the string parameter `sequence` for the result to be greater than 0.
- The string parameters `sequence` and `word` contain only lowercase English letters.
- The length of the string parameter `sequence` is greater than or equal to 1 and is less than or equal to 100.
- The length of the string parameter `word` is greater than or equal to 1 and is less than or equal to 100.